**Delete Your Account**

To delete your account and all associated data, please follow the steps below:

1. Send an email to [dostonlinestore@gmail.com](mailto:dostonlinestore@gmail.com) with the subject "Account Deletion Request".
2. Include your account username and the email address associated with your account in the email body.
3. Specify any additional details that may help us process your request faster.

**Data Retention Information:**
- All your personal data will be permanently deleted from our servers.
- Any data required for legal or regulatory purposes will be retained as per the laws.

If you have any questions, please contact our support team at [dostonlinestore@gmail.com](mailto:dostonlinestore@gmail.com).
